data.description: Here’s your chance to own this Impressive 4 bedrm, 2.5 bathrm home with all the bells & whistles! Features an open layout w/ formal livingrm & diningrm, recessed lights, chair rail molding, large familyroom with wetbar & wine fridge, spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances , granite countertops and plenty of cabinetry. Expansive Fully finished lower level is an entertainer’s dream- the perfect rec room, movie room or 2nd family room; the options are endless! Notable updates include New garbage disposal (2022), new refrigerator (2022), new roof (2016), new plank flooring in basement (2020), new carpet  in family room and bedrooms w/ premium  padding (2019), Large 10x20 shed (2021), painted main level and basement (2020), Insulated family room and attic with foam (2020)  new landscaping (2018). The large deck overlooks the sprawling backyard; perfect for summertime fun! Parking is a breeze with the extra long driveway. Close proximity to plenty of shopping and retail- Foundry Row - LA Fitness 4.2 miles ,Costco   3.1 miles, Trader Joes – 5 miles ,Target  5.4 miles. Move in and enjoy! Welcome home! ** See agent remarks for offer instructions**
